                                                                                                </div>
                        

                        <p>The effort has also been outstanding, Roof said, considering that there have been so many potential excuses for the players to lose their focus.</p>
<p>&ldquo;You&rsquo;re not negative with kids on game day,&rdquo; Roof said. &ldquo;You ask them what they saw, what their thought process was and try and make corrections. You keep them pumped up and keep them going.&rdquo;</p>
